%!PS-Adobe-3.0
%%Title: RERAG two-column invoice demo fixture
%%Creator: hand-written PostScript (regenerate with `ps2pdf two_column_invoice.ps two_column_invoice.pdf`)
%%BoundingBox: 0 0 612 792
%%Pages: 1
%%EndComments

%%Page: 1 1

% Header — single column at the top so the page mixes layouts the way a
% real invoice does. The detector should still call the body section
% k=2 because the bulk of the lines split into two clean clusters.
/Helvetica-Bold findfont 16 scalefont setfont
60 740 moveto (DEMO INVOICE) show

/Helvetica findfont 10 scalefont setfont
60 720 moveto (RERAG educational fixture for relational PDF extraction) show

/Helvetica-Bold findfont 12 scalefont setfont
60 685 moveto (Schedule of charges) show

% Body — two columns. Left column at x=60 (labels), right column at
% x=400 (amounts). 30pt vertical spacing per row, 6 rows. The big
% horizontal gap (340pt) makes adaptive-k k-means an easy win.
/Helvetica findfont 12 scalefont setfont

60  655 moveto (Renewal fee) show
400 655 moveto (EUR 200) show

60  625 moveto (Late payment fee) show
400 625 moveto (EUR 75) show

60  595 moveto (Cancellation fee) show
400 595 moveto (EUR 150) show

60  565 moveto (Reinstatement fee) show
400 565 moveto (EUR 50) show

60  535 moveto (Document copy fee) show
400 535 moveto (EUR 10) show

60  505 moveto (Account closure fee) show
400 505 moveto (EUR 100) show

% Footer — single line at the bottom so the detector sees a Single
% region too on a real page.
/Helvetica findfont 9 scalefont setfont
60 80 moveto (All amounts are illustrative. See the PDF Extraction page in ag for the column tagging.) show

showpage
%%EOF
